// ✅ Redux thunk
dispatch(initializeQuest({ userProgress, storyId }));
```

```tsx
// ❌ New shared button component in Feature/
Feature/Home/components/GradientButton.tsx

// ✅ Extend MainButton or add to UIComponents/
```

```tsx
// ❌ Raw fontSize/fontWeight on standard UI
<Text style={{ fontSize: 16, fontWeight: '600' }} />

// ✅ Font scale
<Text style={Font.subheading.s} />
```

**Exception:** Quest dialog frame text uses `dialogFrameTypography` + `resolveFrameTextColor` from editor `layout_data` — not `Font.*`.

