├── utils/             # Pure functions + __tests__
├── constants/         # Layout constants
└── context/           # QuestReplicaTransitionContext
```

Pure logic → `utils/` or `dialogFrame/` with unit tests in `__tests__/`.

---

## Anti-Patterns

```tsx
// ❌ Fetch chapter/dialog data in component useEffect
useEffect(() => { QuestService.getChapterDetails(...) }, []);

// ❌ Mutate layout_data or frame domain objects
frame.layout_data.position.y = 100;

// ❌ Skip transition hook and swap replica text immediately on prop change
<Text>{replica.text}</Text> // use displayedReplica from transition hook

// ✅ Prefetch and state prep in thunk; UI renders prepared selectors
```

---

## Testing

Co-locate pure logic tests:
- `utils/__tests__/characterSceneGeometry.test.ts`
- `utils/__tests__/characterSceneTransition.test.ts`
- `utils/__tests__/questSceneUtils.test.ts`
- `context/__tests__/questReplicaTransitionOrchestrator.test.ts`

Test geometry, sticky camera, frame transition classification — not snapshot entire components unless necessary.

